OL,3,CElection analysis: Jersey chooses
OL,4,Cstability - but will it last?
OL,6,FThe 2022 election was defined by a
OL,7,Fdesire for change. The 2026 election,
OL,8,Fby contrast, appears to be defined by
OL,9,Fsomething else entirely: stability.
OL,11,FFive of the nine successful Senatorial
OL,12,Fcandidates were members of the current
OL,13,FCouncil of Ministers, suggesting that
OL,14,Fincumbency was rewarded more than it
OL,15,Fwas challenged.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
