OL,3,CElection analysis: Jersey chooses
OL,4,Cstability - but will it last?
OL,6,FTake the strong performances of
OL,7,FExternal Relations Minister Ian Gorst,
OL,8,Fwho finished second in the Senatorial
OL,9,Frace, Chief Minister Lyndon Farnham,
OL,10,Fwho placed third, and Treasury
OL,11,FMinister Elaine Millar, who came
OL,12,Ffourth.
OL,14,FFor Reform Jersey, however, the
OL,15,Felection represents a significant step
OL,16,Fbackwards.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
