OL,3,CElection analysis: Jersey chooses
OL,4,Cstability - but will it last?
OL,6,FThey returned seven candidates, down
OL,7,Ffrom ten at the previous election, and
OL,8,Ffailed to achieve their ambition of
OL,9,Fsecuring a clean sweep in St Helier
OL,10,FSouth.
OL,12,FThis was compounded by leader and co-
OL,13,Ffounder, Sam Mezec, losing his bid for
OL,14,Fa Senatorial seat, while Rob Ward
OL,15,Fmissed out on becoming Constable of St
OL,16,FHelier, with Jersey's most established
OL,17,Fparty now considering a change of name.
OL,26,@uD@Orr
