OL,3,CElection analysis: Jersey chooses
OL,4,Cstability - but will it last?
OL,6,FMore broadly, the results suggest that
OL,7,Fthe momentum behind Reform Jersey's
OL,8,Fanti-establishment message has
OL,9,Fweakened since 2022.
OL,11,FWhere the previous election reflected
OL,12,Fa readiness for political disruption
OL,13,Fand structural change, 2026 instead
OL,14,Fpoints to a more cautious electorate.
OL,16,FBut make no mistake: politics is a
OL,17,Ffickle business and fortunes can shift
OL,18,Fquickly. Remember Kristina Moore?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
