OL,3,CElection analysis: Jersey chooses
OL,4,Cstability - but will it last?
OL,6,FWith the new States Assembly now
OL,7,Ffacing significant challenges - from
OL,8,Fhousing pressures to the high cost of
OL,9,Fliving, and wider concerns about young
OL,10,Fpeople leaving the island - the
OL,11,Fpolitical landscape remains open and
OL,12,Funpredictable.
OL,14,FAnd if stability fails to translate
OL,15,Finto solutions, pressure for more
OL,16,Fradical change could quickly return.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
